structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
GENERAL PROVISIONS APPLICABLE TO COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.catch_line: Real property in development areas not eligible for assessment moratoriums under KRS 99.600.
law.text: Real property located within a development area shall not be eligible for participation in a program granting property assessment or reassessment moratoriums pursuant to KRS 99.600.
law.history: Created 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 95, sec. 14, effective March 23, 2007.
